***Register Form Project***

*Overview*

This project is a simple User Registration Form built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. 
It validates user inputs like username, email, password, and confirm password, ensuring proper data entry before submission.

Features

âœ… Responsive design with modern UI
âœ… Validation for empty fields, email format, password length, and password matching
âœ… Success and error handling with visual feedback
âœ… Uses JavaScript for real-time validation

Technologies Used

HTML5 - Structure of the form

CSS3 - Styling and responsive design

JavaScript - Form validation

