How to Use

Clone the repository:

git clone <repository-url>

Open index.html in a browser.

Enter user details and test the validation.

Validation Rules

Username: Required.

Email: Must be a valid email format.

Password: At least 8 characters long.

Confirm Password: Must match the entered password.

Example Validation Messages

ðŸ”´ "Username is required" - If the username field is empty.
ðŸ”´ "Please enter a valid email" - If the email format is incorrect.
ðŸ”´ "Password must be at least 8 characters long" - If password is too short.
ðŸ”´ "Password does not match" - If confirm password doesnâ€™t match.
